################# DAPR Guts

## Check and wait for side car to respond , wait for  10 secs
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/Sidecar/10

### Check side car health along with app health
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/SidecarHealth

### Check side car health only
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/SidecarPartialHealth

### Get configuration values using Dapr API
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/ConfigValues

### Get secrets from a multivalued secret store
#(local & docker, multivalue=true)
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/SecretValues/layered

### Set state
POST {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/StateValues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Key": "Key1",
  "Value": "Key1-Value"
}

### Get state values
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/StateValues/Key1

### Call the same API Cron binding is calling 
POST {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/digicron

###  remove sidecar from the pod
# DELETE {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/Sidecar

### Call a non-dapr service using Dapr Http API
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/NonDaprEpResiliency/001

### Call a Dapr service using Dapr Http API
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/DaprEpResiliency/SuperWomen

### Call an endpoint that times out.
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/Delayed/2

### Call an endpoint that throws 500
GET {{Digitizing_HostAddress}}/api/dapr/Fault/false

